chapters.title: Digits of Pi mapped to E flat major (3, 1, 4, 1, 5, 9, 2, 6, 5, 3, 5)
Drums and bass hammer out 3, then 1, then 4, then 1
Digits of Pi return in E flat, but neither a major nor minor scale
